data.meta_description: Versatile voice artist, mimic, character actor.  Credits include The Octonauts, Thomas and Friends, Angelina Ballerina, The Koala Brothers, Watch My Chops.
data.text:
Keith Wickham

Voices - Characters - Audio restoration

A veteran of over 1500 animation voice

sessions, hundreds of commercials and video games,

with a background in acting and comedy.

A versatile and experienced voice artist,

writer, producer and editor with a fully

equipped home studio.

Animation credits include Thomas and Friends

(Fat Controller, Gordon, Henry, Salty, Edward and others)

The Octonauts (Shellington, Inkling and many others)

Watch My Chops (Corneil), 64 Zoo Lane (Nelson and others)

The Koala Brothers (Frank, Archie, Sammy)

The Mr Men (Mr Tall and Mr Small)
